               <lb facs="#facs_3_l_1" n="N002"/>1. Perceptive: {<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__3888">Fra Angelico</rs>,<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__496"> Dürer,</rs> Fortuna (<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__496">Dürers </rs>Holzschnitte, table 19.)} Caritas, Brinkmann, 359.
               <lb facs="#facs_3_l_2" n="N003"/>2. Participant: Buddha (Dietz, 117)
