               <lb facs="#facs_3_l_4" n="N005"/>Opening souls: <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1550">Raffael</rs>, Madonna, (Photograph)
               <lb facs="#facs_3_l_5" n="N006"/>p. 27. Expressing
               <lb facs="#facs_3_l_6" n="N007"/><rs type="keyword" ref="#Expressionism">Expressionism</rs>: Crucifixion,
